companyName: USAA MSCI International Value Momentum Blend Index
description:
The investment seeks to provide investment results that correspond to the MSCI World ex USA Select Value Momentum Blend Index.
 The fund seeks to achieve its investment objective by investing at least 80% of its net assets in securities in the index, depositary receipts on securities in the index, and securities underlying depositary receipts in the index. The index is designed to deliver exposure to equity market performance in non-U.S. markets and provide higher exposure to value and momentum factors within the MSCI World ex USA Index while also maintaining moderate index turnover and lower realized volatility than traditional capitalization weighted indexes.
